<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id5a801f1e-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c" identifier="/us/usc/t29/s761"><num value="761">§ 761.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated to carry out this subchapter $103,970,000 for fiscal year 2015, $112,001,000 for fiscal year 2016, $114,325,000 for fiscal year 2017, $116,860,000 for fiscal year 2018, $119,608,000 for fiscal year 2019, and $122,143,000 for fiscal year 2020.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id5a801f1f-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c">(<ref href="/us/pl/93/112/tII/s201">Pub. L. 93–112, title II, § 201</ref>, as added <ref href="/us/pl/105/220/tIV/s405">Pub. L. 105–220, title IV, § 405</ref>, <date date="1998-08-07">Aug. 7, 1998</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/112/1168">112 Stat. 1168</ref>; amended <ref href="/us/pl/105/277/dA/s101/f/tVIII/s401/16">Pub. L. 105–277, div. A, § 101(f) [title VIII, § 401(16)]</ref>, <date date="1998-10-21">Oct. 21, 1998</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/112/2681-337">112 Stat. 2681–337</ref>, 2681–412; <ref href="/us/pl/113/128/tIV/s432">Pub. L. 113–128, title IV, § 432</ref>, <date date="2014-07-22">July 22, 2014</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/128/1660">128 Stat. 1660</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
