<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id5a801f21-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="priorProvisions" id="id5a801f22-3a70-11f1-8704-e0e66b400d7c"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Prior Provisions</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Prior sections 761 to 761b were omitted in the general amendment of this subchapter by <ref href="/us/pl/105/220">Pub. L. 105–220</ref>.</p>
